Package edu.umn.se.trap.exception

Exception Summary
BusinessLogicException An exception representing a problem found while processing a business logic rule.
FormProcessorException An exception referencing a problem encountered while processing a form that isn't related to input validation, buisness logic.
FormStorageException An exception relating to the operation of the form storage sub-system
InputValidationException An exception representing an error during input validation.
InsufficientFundsException An exception the means that there are insufficient funds for a reimbursement.
MissingFieldException Exception meaning that a field is missing on the input form which is preventing for submission/processing from moving forward.
TRAPException  
TRAPRuntimeException A general runtime exception in the TRAP system.
